creator: Nect
descriptionHtml:
Nect Selfie Ident - The next generation of digital identity verification.

Many companies are required by law to verify the identity of their users. Traditional verification methods do not provide a satisfactory solution. By letter it takes far too long. A video identity is not always available and does not fit every situation. And let's be honest: Who knows their identity card pin?

But there is another way. With the Nect App, identification is quick and easy - at any time.

First you record a selfie video. Then record the front of your ID document. And finally, take a photo of the back of the document. That's it!

Nect evaluates your data in a multi-secured process and follows the strictest data protection criteria.

After the successful evaluation of your data, you continue the registration on the website of your service provider.

Online identification has never been easier - via Selfie Ident. Enjoy your day - with Nect!

title: Nect

creator: Nect
descriptionHtml:
Identify yourself without a personal appointment or extensive correspondence and without the need of a PIN or an unpleasant video chat with an agent. Nect is the user-friendly solution for fully automated online identification that meets the highest security standards and works without waiting time - no matter where, no matter when.

In just three steps you can have your identity verified. All you need is an ID document, a smartphone with a working camera and yourself.

How does it work?

1. Record a video of the front of the ID document.
2. Take a photo of the back of the ID document.
3. Take a selfie video and read out two randomly shown words.

Once your identity has been successfully verified by Nect, you can continue with the registration process on our partner company's app or website.

What's on the horizon?

Once you have completed your identification process, keep the Nect app on your mobile device. After initial identification, we will create your personal Nect ID for you, which you can use in future to identify yourself even more quickly for our wide network of partner companies.

descriptionHtml:
Identify yourself quickly and securely or sign confidential documents - at any time and from anywhere. Without a personal appointment or extensive correspondence, without a PIN or video chat with a service agent. In the Nect Wallet, you can store your digital identity securely and have it at your disposal at all times. Whether it's your ID card, passport, driving licence or other ID documents. Use our user-friendly, fully automated solution to identify yourself at our partner companies in a legally compliant manner. Our Nect Wallet meets the highest security standards and is available without waiting time.

Have your identity verified and confirmed in just three steps. All you need is an ID document and a smartphone with a camera.

Take a video of your ID documents front.

Take a photo of your ID documents back.

Take a video of your face and read out the two randomly displayed words.

Once your identity has been successfully verified by Nect, you can continue your registration process in our partner company's app or on their website.

What else can you expect from us?

Once successfully identified, your ID document will be digitally and securely stored in the Nect Wallet. For your next identification, you can simply reuse the ID document within seconds via facial recognition. Our network of partner companies is constantly growing. So keep the Nect Wallet on your mobile phone and use your digital identity for other companies in the future - it's worth it!

Without a personal appointment or extensive correspondence, without a PIN or video chat with a service agent. In the Nect Wallet, you can store your digital identity securely and have it at your disposal at all times. Whether it's your ID card, passport, driving licence or other ID documents. Use our user-friendly, fully automated solution to identify yourself at our partner companies in a legally compliant manner. Our Nect Wallet meets the highest security standards and is available without waiting time.

Have your identity verified and confirmed in just three steps. All you need is an ID document and a smartphone with a camera.

Take a video of your ID documents front.

Take a photo of your ID documents back.

Take a video of your face and read out the two randomly displayed words.

Once your identity has been successfully verified by Nect, you can continue your registration process in our partner company's app or on their website.

What else can you expect from us?

Once successfully identified, your ID document will be digitally and securely stored in the Nect Wallet. For your next identification, you can simply reuse the ID document within seconds via facial recognition. Our network of partner companies is constantly growing. So keep the Nect Wallet on your mobile phone and use your digital identity for other companies in the future - it's worth it!

Without a personal appointment or extensive correspondence, without a PIN or video chat with a service agent. In the Nect Wallet, you can store your digital identity securely and have it at your disposal at all times. Whether it's your ID card, passport, driving licence or other ID documents. Use our user-friendly, fully automated solution to identify yourself at our partner companies in a legally compliant manner. Our Nect Wallet meets the highest security standards and is available without waiting time.

Have your identity verified and confirmed in just three steps. All you need is an ID document and a smartphone with a camera.

Take a video of your ID documents front.

Take a photo of your ID documents back.

Take a video of your face and read out the two randomly displayed words.

Once your identity has been successfully verified by Nect, you can continue your registration process in our partner company's app or on their website.

What else can you expect from us?

Once successfully identified, your ID document will be digitally and securely stored in the Nect Wallet. For your next identification, you can simply reuse the ID document within seconds via facial recognition. Our network of partner companies is constantly growing. So keep the Nect Wallet on your mobile phone and use your digital identity for other companies in the future - it's worth it!
